replies.body:
Varus (with or without {{item:3070}} ) is God-tier in ARAM

My preference is an Armor Pen-heavy build - sure, it's less damage later in the game when everyone's nearly full build, but oh my god the midgame powerspike is retarded

I go {{item:3070}} into {{item:3134}} 
Finish {{item:3004}} , then look at enemy builds

If heavy armor, get {{item:3035}} 
If not much armor, finish {{item:3142}} 
Either way, you next get {{item:3508}} or {{item:3072}} (if you have 10% CDR from runes/masteries, take BT - if not, take Essence)

By now, your Q should be chunking squishies for about half of their Health, more if you can get some W procs off. xD

Full build usually looks something like this

{{item:3042}} {{item:3142}} {{item:3035}} {{item:3508}} {{item:3071}} (lol what are boots)

Last item is a tossup depending on enemy team

Full of squishies, easy to blow up? {{item:3078}}  or {{item:3031}} or {{item:3072}} (if you took Essence Reaver)
Lots of long ranged AP poke and need defense? {{item:3102}}  or {{item:3156}} or {{item:3139}} 
Lots of divers and need peel? {{item:3153}} or {{item:3083}} or {{item:3143}} or {{item:3157}} (yeah, I've done Zhonya's before, it works well against heavy diver dudes like Talon)
Is there a Teemo/Evelynn/Shaco and no one on your team is taking vision? {{item:3185}}

***
